data.description: This property is professionally marketed by Chris Harrison. Please call 575-496-0141 for information, or check out my website at: www.searchlascruces.com. Home with magnificant views of the Mesilla Valley,City lights and Organ Mountains! Sit on the patio with a cup of coffee and watch the sun come up! this Enclosed backyard and room for horses! Easy care landscaping, circular drive , front and back covered porch and patio. This home has 4 BR's, 2 baths, 2 living areas and a country kitchen with lots of cabinets, pantry and eating area. Master bedroom has large walk-in closet with built-in shelving between master bedroom and master bath. 4th bedroom has built-in cabinets, and door leading into garage and would make great hobby room, office or game room. Living room with fireplace, beams and wood floor. Real wood floors in the living room and master bedroom. Large patio with doors leading out from family room and hallway off of living room! For Immediate Info text: 51004, Message: E03458.
